'''方斯華·賈克柏'''（{{lang-fr|'''François Jacob'''}}，{{bd|1920年|6月17日|2013年|4月19日|catIdx=Jacob}}）是一位[[猶太|猶太]]裔[[法國|法國]][[生物學家|生物學家]]，他與[[賈克·莫諾|賈克·莫諾]]發現了[[酶|酶]]在[[原核生物|原核生物]][[轉錄作用|轉錄作用]]調控中的角色，也就是後來所知的[[乳糖操縱組|乳糖操縱組]]。兩人與[[安德列·利沃夫|安德列·利沃夫]]共同獲得了1965年的[[諾貝爾生理學或醫學獎|諾貝爾生理學或醫學獎]]<ref name="natureobit">{{Cite journal | last1 = Morange | first1 = Michel | title = François Jacob (1920–2013) French freedom fighter who helped to uncover how genes are regulated| doi = 10.1038/497440a | journal = Nature | volume = 497 | issue = 7450 | pages = 440 | year = 2013 | pmid =  23698437| pmc = }}</ref><ref name=rsbm>{{cite journal|last1=Jacob|first1=F.|last2=Girard|first2=M.|title=Andre Michel Lwoff. 8 May 1902-30 September 1994|journal=Biographical Memoirs of Fellows of the Royal Society|volume=44|year=1998|pages=255–263|issn=0080-4606|doi=10.1098/rsbm.1998.0017|pmid=11623983}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2013/04/21/nobel-winning-biologist-francois-jacob-dies-at-92/ |title=Nobel-winning biologist Francois Jacob dies at 92 |publisher=The Raw Story |date= |accessdate=2013-04-22 |archive-date=2014-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140909090851/http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2013/04/21/nobel-winning-biologist-francois-jacob-dies-at-92/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=formemrs>{{cite journal|last1=Morange|first1=Michel|title=François Jacob. 17 June 1920 — 19 April 2013|journal=[[Biographical_Memoirs_of_Fellows_of_the_Royal_Society|Biographical Memoirs of Fellows of the Royal Society]]|publisher=[[Royal_Society|Royal Society]]|location=London|year=2017|pages=rsbm20160021|issn=0080-4606|doi=10.1098/rsbm.2016.0021}}</ref>。

賈克柏後來又與[[悉尼·布伦纳|悉尼·布伦纳]]（2002年因[[線蟲|線蟲]]研究而獲得諾貝爾獎）提出了[[核糖體|核糖體]]進行[[轉譯|轉譯]]時的作用方式假說，並由後來的實驗證實<ref>Robert F. Weaver. ''Molecular biology'' 3rd edition. McGraw-Hill. ISBN 0-07-284611-9.</ref>。1996年，賈克柏成為[[法蘭西學術院|法蘭西學術院]]院士。2013年4月19日逝世。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2013/04/21/nobel-winning-biologist-francois-jacob-dies-at-92/ |title=Nobel-winning biologist Francois Jacob dies at 92 |work=rawstory.com |language=en |date=2013-04-21 |accessdate=2013-04-22 |archive-date=2014-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140909090851/http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2013/04/21/nobel-winning-biologist-francois-jacob-dies-at-92/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

